    Details, Size & Software

    Rhinokey Smartcard is the thinnest tracker that works worldwide with both iPhone and Samsung devices. Connect it via Apple Find My or Google’s Find Hub app.

    Dimensions: 85 x 54 x 1.8 mm (3.3 x 2.1 x 0.07 inch)

    Questions?

    We've got answers

    Why you will love Rhinokey® Smartcard.

    Just don't worry about losing your items. Made to an extreme thinness of 1.8 mm, it fits easily into your wallet and small spaces. Designed for Apple Find My or Google Find Hub, it lasts up to 5 months on a single charge.

    Can you track it worldwide?

    If an Apple or Android device is nearby or has been nearby, it will use that signal for locating. This works worldwide.

    Is the battery rechargeable?

    Yes, Rhinokey® Smartcard can be recharged using Qi wireless charging. Don't worry about needing to buy a new card every year as these are rechargeable and re-used.

    Does Rhinokey® Smartcard work in RFID blocking wallets?

    Yes, it has been tested in RFID wallets and it is still able to connect with your phone. For best connectivity, place the Smartcard on the pocket closest to the outside of the wallet.

    What is the range?

    The range can extend up to 210 ft (65 m) when there is a clear line of sight from your phone to the Rhinokey Smartcard. Ring to find it in that range.

    Android supports precision finding, meaning you can find your Smartcard by moving closer to it and seeing this in the app.

    Does it work with Android?

    Yes, it does! It will work with Google Find Hub, which can be downloaded from the Play Store.
